Based on that alone, investment will be higher.
 The only reason that interest rates are higher - is because the demand
 for investment has increased, and one needs to 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

pay higher price
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 to 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

convince
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 the supply to grow accordingly.
\end_layout

