The liquidity demand (for real purchasing power):
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\frac{M}{P}\right)^{d}=L^{d}\left(\begin{array}{c}
Y\\
(+)
\end{array},\begin{array}{c}
r\\
(-)
